, \"to\": 415}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It mostly applies to people driving, but even pedestrians will need to show a QR code to enter an area called the 'grey zone' around the River Seine in the centre, where the opening ceremony will take place.\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 555, \"end\": 566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 445}, {\"ngram\": \"even pedestrians\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 475}, {\"ngram\": \"a QR code\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 503}, {\"ngram\": \"an area\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'grey zone\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 542}, {\"ngram\": \"the centre\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 580}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 608}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The codes will be checked at access points along the entrance to each zone, manned by officers.\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 722, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The codes\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"access points\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 669}, {\"ngram\": \"the entrance\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"each zone\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"officers\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Applications for the passesopened today, with people needing to upload various documents to be authorised.\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Applications\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"various documents\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony grey zone will be in place 24 hours a day for an eight-day period from July 18 to July 26.\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 853, \"end\": 862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grey-zone_(international_relations)\", \"score\": 0.9999981366787858, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"grey zone\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grey-zone_(international_relations)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grey-zone_(international_relations)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"an eight-day period\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 918}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 939}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the official start of the games, this zone will be lifted but drivers will still need to show their pass at the perimeters of the 'red' and 'blue' zones which cover significant areas of the city, while grey zones will cover the exact areas where events are taking place.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1153, \"end\": 1163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aegean_dispute\", \"score\": 0.9999999932902028, \"rank\": 6.709836871575405e-09, \"text\": \"grey zones\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aegean_dispute\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aegean_dispute\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the official start\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 969}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 982}, {\"ngram\": \"this zone\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 993}, {\"ngram\": \"drivers\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"their pass\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"the perimeters\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'red' and 'blue' zones\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"significant areas\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1133}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"the exact areas\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1220}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The policy has echoes of the 'Covid pass' system during the pandemic, when many countries introduced QR code passes stored on phone apps, for people to prove they had been vaccinated and access certain venues or transport.\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The policy\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1233}, {\"ngram\": \"echoes\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'Covid pass' system\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1271}, {\"ngram\": \"the pandemic\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"many countries\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1312}, {\"ngram\": \"QR code passes\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"phone apps\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1371}, {\"ngram\": \"certain venues\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"transport\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To be granted a pass, people must show proof of identity, an identity photo, their address, and potentially other documents including vehicle registration document or proof of their employer.\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1638, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pass\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1467}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"proof\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1491}, {\"ngram\": \"identity\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"an identity photo\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1522}, {\"ngram\": \"their address\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"potentially other documents\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"vehicle registration document\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"proof\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1619}, {\"ngram\": \"their employer\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes after high profile terror attacks in France, including anattack on Bastille Day celebrations in Nicewhere 86 were killed, and coordinated attacks in 2015 including onthe Bataclan concert hall which left 130 people dead.\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1686, \"end\": 1692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9989924611354738, \"rank\": 0.00033861562633607904, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1819, \"end\": 1827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/November_2015_Paris_attacks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.555935894006942e-36, \"text\": \"Bataclan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/November_2015_Paris_attacks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/November_2015_Paris_attacks\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high profile terror attacks\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1682}, {\"ngram\": \"anattack\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1712}, {\"ngram\": \"Bastille Day celebrations\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1741}, {\"ngram\": \"Nicewhere\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"coordinated attacks\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"130 people\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The UK government warns that terrorists are 'very likely to try to carry out attacks in France', saying methods have included knife attacks, shootings, bombings and vehicle attacks.\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 2051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1874, \"end\": 1887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999994056727627, \"rank\": 5.282253213718492e-06, \"text\": \"UK government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_the_United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1958, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9989924611354738, \"rank\": 0.00033861